---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Organization | Agora" description="Understanding the distributed structure and the sponsor system of our community.">
  
  <section class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 text-zinc-100">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-20">
      
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">The Structure</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400">
          Agora’s structure combines the resilience of interpersonal bonds with the power of mass organization.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/10 text-white text-xs font-mono">Level 01: The Bond</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">The Sponsor System</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
            No one enters Agora alone. Every new member is paired with a <strong>Sponsor</strong>—a seasoned member who acts as a guide and an accountability partner.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-4">
           <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
           <div class="w-px h-8 bg-white/20"></div>
           <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white text-black flex items-center justify-center font-bold">You</div>
           <p class="text-sm font-mono text-zinc-500 uppercase">Direct Accountability</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/10 text-white text-xs font-mono">Level 02: The Cell</div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Distributed Chapters</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
              Chapters are local, autonomous nodes capped at <strong>Dunbar's Number</strong> to ensure every member actually knows everyone else.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-4">
          <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto h-80 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-zinc-800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <line x1="50%" y1="10%" x2="90%" y2="40%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
              <line x1="90%" y1="40%" x2="75%" y2="90%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
              <line x1="75%" y1="90%" x2="25%" y2="90%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
              <line x1="25%" y1="90%" x2="10%" y2="40%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
              <line x1="10%" y1="40%" x2="50%" y2="10%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" />
              <line x1="50%" y1="10%" x2="25%" y2="90%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4" />
              <line x1="90%" y1="40%" x2="10%" y2="40%" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4" />
            </svg>
            <div class="relative z-10 w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-white text-black flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold uppercase">
              <span>Local Cell</span>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute top-[10%] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-[40%] right-[10%] w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[25%] w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] left-[25%] w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[10%] w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-zinc-800 border border-white/20"></div>
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-white/10 text-white text-xs font-mono">Level 03: The Movement</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Global Coordination</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        While action is local, our strategy is global. Regional nodes connect to <strong>Central Leadership</strong> to synchronize efforts against neoliberal hegemony. 
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
        The Hub provides the "Social Network" infrastructure, legal support, and unified messaging, ensuring that thousands of autonomous chapters move as one cohesive force for social change.
      </p>
    </div>
          <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center space-y-4">
    <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg mx-auto h-80 flex items-center justify-center">
      <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-zinc-800" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="50%" y2="15%" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
        <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="85%" y2="35%" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
        <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="80%" y2="75%" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
        <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="20%" y2="75%" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
        <line x1="50%" y1="50%" x2="15%" y2="35%" stroke="white" stroke-width="1" stroke-opacity="0.3" />
        
        <path d="M 50,15 Q 85,35 80,75 Q 20,75 15,35 Q 50,15" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4" />
      </svg>

      <div class="relative z-10 w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-white text-black flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-2 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)]">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none mb-1">Central</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase">Leadership</span>
      </div>

      <div class="absolute top-[15%] left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-400">EU</div>
      <div class="absolute top-[35%] right-[15%] w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-400">NA</div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[25%] right-[20%] w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-400">AS</div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[25%] left-[20%] w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-400">AF</div>
      <div class="absolute top-[35%] left-[15%] w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-white/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[8px] font-mono text-zinc-400">SA</div>
    </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

      <div id="map-section" class="space-y-8 pt-12 border-t border-zinc-800">
        <div class="text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Active Nodes</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 mt-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">The movement is spreading</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative w-full aspect-video bg-zinc-950 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden">
        <div 
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-800"
          style="mask-image: url('/world.svg'); mask-size: contain; mask-repeat: no-repeat; mask-position: center; -webkit-mask-image: url('/world.svg'); -webkit-mask-size: contain; -webkit-mask-repeat: no-repeat; -webkit-mask-position: center;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative w-full aspect-video bg-zinc-950 rounded-3xl border border-white/5 overflow-hidden">
  <img 
    src="/world.svg" 
    alt="Movement Map" 
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain opacity-10"
  />

  <svg class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full text-white/20" viewBox="0 0 100 100" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <line x1="25" y1="40" x2="48" y2="30" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.2" stroke-dasharray="1" />
    
    </svg>

  <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[25%]">
    <span class="absolute inline-flex h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-white animate-ping-slow opacity-75"></span>
    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-white"></span>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute top-[30%] left-[48%]">
    <span class="absolute inline-flex h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-white animate-ping-slow opacity-75"></span>
    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-white"></span>
  </div>
</div>

          <div class="absolute top-[30%] left-[48%]">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-white animate-ping-slow opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-white"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute top-[40%] left-[25%]">
            <span class="absolute inline-flex h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-white animate-ping-slow opacity-75"></span>
            <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-3 w-3 bg-white"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 italic">
          Exact locations are only visible to verified members via the Social Network app.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>